OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775160364
OL,3,CBelfast music teacher charged with
OL,4,Ctrafficking and teen sex abuse offences
OL,6,FA musical tutor who worked at schools
OL,7,Facross Belfast is facing prosecution
OL,8,Fover allegations he trafficked and
OL,9,Fdrugged a teenage boy for sexual
OL,10,Fpurposes.
OL,12,FRobert James Briscoe appeared in court
OL,13,Ftoday charged with eight separate
OL,14,Fcharges.
OL,16,FThe 48-year-old has now been suspended
OL,17,Ffrom his job with the Education
OL,18,FAuthority (EA), a judge was told.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
