PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775160364
OL,3,CBelfast music teacher charged with
OL,4,Ctrafficking and teen sex abuse offences
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Education
OL,7,FAuthority said: "The Education
OL,8,FAuthority is aware of the active court
OL,9,Fproceedings and it would not be
OL,10,Fappropriate for us to comment on the
OL,11,Fdetails of the case.
OL,13,F"The safety and protection of children
OL,14,Fis our highest priority and where we
OL,15,Fare aware of any concerns we take all
OL,16,Fappropriate steps in conjunction with
OL,17,Frelevant agencies."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
