FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775160364
OL,3,CBelfast music teacher charged with
OL,4,Ctrafficking and teen sex abuse offences
OL,6,FBriscoe, with an address at Seamount
OL,7,Fin Belfast, faces two counts of human
OL,8,Ftrafficking to exploit the teenager,
OL,9,Fpaying sexual services of a child, and
OL,10,Fa further attempt to pay for sexual
OL,11,Fservices.
OL,13,FHe is also accused of administering a
OL,14,Fsubstance with sexual intent,
OL,15,Fpossessing Class A Methamphetamine
OL,16,Fwith intent to supply, and having a
OL,17,Fseparate quantity of Class B drugs.
OL,19,FThe alleged offences were committed on
OL,20,Fdates between September 30, 2025 and
OL,21,FMarch 10 this year.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
