FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775160364
OL,3,CBelfast music teacher charged with
OL,4,Ctrafficking and teen sex abuse offences
OL,6,FBriscoe's work for the EA involved
OL,7,Facting as a peripatetic brass tutor in
OL,8,Fschools across the city.
OL,10,FHe also helped to run the City of
OL,11,FBelfast Youth Orchestra and was a
OL,12,Fdirector at music at Helen's Bay
OL,13,FPresbyterian Church.
OL,15,FIn a further role, he worked as a
OL,16,Ffreelance travel consultant on music
OL,17,Ftours for schools and colleges
OL,18,Fthroughout the United Kingdom.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
