OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775160364
OL,3,CBelfast music teacher charged with
OL,4,Ctrafficking and teen sex abuse offences
OL,6,FThere is no connection between the
OL,7,Falleged victim and any positions held
OL,8,Fby Briscoe.
OL,10,FAppearing for the first time at
OL,11,FBelfast Magistrates' Court, he
OL,12,Fconfirmed that he understood the
OL,13,Fcharges against him.
OL,15,FAn investigating detective said he
OL,16,Fcould connect him to all of the
OL,17,Falleged offences.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
