PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775160364
OL,3,CBelfast music teacher charged with
OL,4,Ctrafficking and teen sex abuse offences
OL,6,FDefence solicitor Adrian Harvey
OL,7,Findicated that his client's job with
OL,8,Fthe EA could now be in further
OL,9,Fjeopardy.
OL,11,F"Mr Briscoe's current employer will
OL,12,Fmore than likely take a certain
OL,13,Fcourse," he predicted.
OL,15,F"He's on a precautionary suspension at
OL,16,Fthe minute, but I think it's
OL,17,Finevitable following today's hearing
OL,18,Fwhat will happen.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@HO]wD@AOU
