OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1775160364
OL,3,CBelfast music teacher charged with
OL,4,Ctrafficking and teen sex abuse offences
OL,6,FReleasing the defendant on continuing
OL,7,Fbail, District Judge Anne Marshall
OL,8,Fbanned him from contacting the injured
OL,9,Fparty or anyone else aged under 18.
OL,11,FShe also imposed a further prohibition
OL,12,Fon having any device which can access
OL,13,Fthe internet.
